OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772741481
OL,3,CFirst flight bringing Brits trapped in
OL,4,Cthe Middle East lands in Birmingham
OL,6,FThe first Brits flown to Birmingham
OL,7,Ffrom the Middle East since the start
OL,8,Fof the war with Iran, have arrived
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,FThe flight landed at Birmingham
OL,12,FAirport at 12:53, more than an hour
OL,13,Flater than planned.
OL,15,FThere is also a flight scheduled to
OL,16,Fdepart from Birmingham Airport for
OL,17,FDubai at 13:40 today.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
