OL,3,CFirst flight bringing Brits trapped in
OL,4,Cthe Middle East lands in Birmingham
OL,6,FTravel to the region is still
OL,7,Frestricted, with flights to gulf and
OL,8,Fconnecting flights to India still
OL,9,Fcancelled.
OL,11,FThe most recent statement from
OL,12,FEmirates, issued on the 3rd of March,
OL,13,Fsays:
OL,15,F"All scheduled Emirates flights to and
OL,16,Ffrom Dubai remain suspended until
OL,17,F2359hrs UAE time on 4 March, due to
OL,18,Fairspace closures across the region.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772741481
OL,3,CFirst flight bringing Brits trapped in
OL,4,Cthe Middle East lands in Birmingham
OL,6,F"Emirates continues to operate a
OL,7,Flimited number of passenger
OL,8,Frepatriation and freighter flights on
OL,9,F3 and 4 March.
OL,11,F"We are accommodating customers with
OL,12,Fearlier bookings as a priority on
OL,13,Fthese limited flights.
OL,15,F"Please do not go to the airport
OL,16,Funless you have been notified directly
OL,17,Fby Emirates or hold a confirmed
OL,18,Fbooking for these flights."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
