PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772741481
OL,3,CFirst flight bringing Brits trapped in
OL,4,Cthe Middle East lands in Birmingham
OL,6,FThe airline has asked customers to
OL,7,Fcheck its website for updates and said
OL,8,Fthe safety of its customers and crew
OL,9,Fis its "highest priority".
OL,11,FThe Foreign Office updated its travel
OL,12,Fadvice for Thailand early on
OL,13,FWednesday, 4th March, "due to the
OL,14,Fescalation in the Middle East".
OL,16,FIt said in a statement: "Escalation in
OL,17,Fthe Middle East has caused widespread
OL,18,Ftravel disruption, including airspace
OL,19,Fclosures, delayed and cancelled
OL,20,Fflights.
OL,26,@uD@WOUvD@^O]xD@YOU
