PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772741481
OL,3,CFirst flight bringing Brits trapped in
OL,4,Cthe Middle East lands in Birmingham
OL,6,F"Your travel plans may be affected,
OL,7,Feven if your destination is not in the
OL,8,FMiddle East."
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FElsewhere, the first government flight
OL,16,Fis going to leave Oman on Wednesday
OL,17,Fevening as the government scrambles to
OL,18,Fevacuate citizens from the region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]
