OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772741481
OL,3,CFirst flight bringing Brits trapped in
OL,4,Cthe Middle East lands in Birmingham
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office said the flight
OL,7,Fwill depart the country's capital,
OL,8,FMuscat, at 7pm and is available for
OL,9,FBritish nationals, their partners and
OL,10,Fchildren under 18 with a valid travel
OL,11,Fdocument.
